song.title: Funky Fajitas
song.info: (From [url]www.sunspire-records.com[/url] ) [quote] This was my entry for this year's 'Main#5 Demoparty' in Marseille, France - composed just hours before the deadline. It placed 13th, short on the competition but despite that it was still tremendous fun and I hope some people might find it enjoyable[/quote]
